journeys/sports-adventure">Sports + Adventure</a></li><li><a class="_1EOMzBWaKWJY08qS8c9Ngh" href="https://www.afar.com/journeys/trips-with-friends">Trips with Friends</a></li><li><a class="_1EOMzBWaKWJY08qS8c9Ngh" href="https://www.afar.com/journeys/wellness">Wellness</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></li><li class="_1COXYUiVAHFHacT1JwTZ6_"><a class="_3Uvpq35_gHYo1zkX2wdNhs" href="https://www.afar.com/journeys">Subscribe</a><div class="dropdown"><button type="button"><i class="_1xxwKoVqAaQ7FYmg-3h6Z9 _1ZiDatsNqG3NkFIpfp1olu"></i></button><div class="_2biLEvHSI5qomQgI9cYbbg sEs_yuamxK9EGrm6NfJDi _1ouBolls5WmhrPifJEvpmo"><div class="_3xZf5JXG5Q0sMG7o-bkXQy _2c5gb5L7MhVF9KOAYBRLU2"><div class="_1gZ5uykNxIKtdgx6f9qRf"><div class="_3pe9jsNfrNQ-mz8fawrvT1"><a class="_29w2BQ5uhyVwW5ocAuNuSQ" href="https://www.afar.com/newsletters">Sign up for our newsletter</a></div><div class="_3pe9jsNfrNQ-mz8fawrvT1"><a class="_29w2BQ5uhyVwW5ocAuNuSQ" href="https://w1.buysub.com/servlet/OrdersGateway?cds_mag_code=AFA&amp;cds_page_id=223701&amp;cds_response_key=I8300">Subscribe to magazine</a></div><div class="_3pe9jsNfrNQ-mz8fawrvT1"><a class="_29w2BQ5uhyVwW5ocAuNuSQ" href="https://w1.buysub.com/servlet/GiftsGateway?cds_mag_code=AFA&amp;cds_page_id=224551&amp;cds_responsekey=G8301">Give a gift</a></div><div class="_3pe9jsNfrNQ-mz8fawrvT1"><a class="_29w2BQ5uhyVwW5ocAuNuSQ" href="https://w1.buysub.com/pubs/AF/AFA/login.jsp?cds_page_id=63692&amp;cds_mag_code=AFA&amp;id=1509056517468&amp;lsid=72991721019048892&amp;vid=4">Renew</a></div><div class="_3pe9jsNfrNQ-mz8fawrvT1"><a class="_29w2BQ5uhyVwW5ocAuNuSQ" href="https://w1.buysub.com/pubs/AF/AFA/login.jsp?cds_page_id=63692&amp;cds_mag_code=AFA&amp;id=1562279604262&amp;lsid=91851732075041154&amp;vid=3">Customer Service</a></div></div></div></div></div></li></ul><span></span></div><div class="_3aXlR_VQB6bvs9akofIBwk"><button aria-label="Where do you want to go?" class="_2qNMDX6LXcm61j5OFVZZ85" type="button"><i class="_1xxwKoV