">Travel News</p></a></div><div class="_20HsJcI5gSjDrdcr6MqId2 _1gZ5uykNxIKtdgx6f9qRf _1ggJ0o9uWv5bOTWfFdkqUH"><a aria-label="26 Independent Bookstores in the U.S. That We Love" data-gtm-event="article-related-content-module" data-gtm-label="afar" href="/magazine/the-best-independent-bookstores-in-the-united-states"><img alt="26 Independent Bookstores in the U.S. That We Love" class="rwtN4FvkMLZTY1gX7n3v4 _1MwUyUNFpNtn27W7qYmqk0" data-src="https://afar-production.imgix.net/uploads/content_items/images/LxHGLYYy7b/original_35b5cadc11af7c54a26ff5b92e11b6d9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=top&amp;lossless=true&amp;w=500&amp;h=313" data-srcset="https://afar-production.imgix.net/uploads/content_items/images/LxHGLYYy7b/original_35b5cadc11af7c54a26ff5b92e11b6d9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=top&amp;lossless=true&amp;w=500&amp;h=313&amp;dpr=1 1x,https://afar-production.imgix.net/uploads/content_items/images/LxHGLYYy7b/original_35b5cadc11af7c54a26ff5b92e11b6d9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=top&amp;lossless=true&amp;w=500&amp;h=313&amp;dpr=2 2x,https://afar-production.imgix.net/uploads/content_items/images/LxHGLYYy7b/original_35b5cadc11af7c54a26ff5b92e11b6d9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=top&amp;lossless=true&amp;w=500&amp;h=313&amp;dpr=3 3x" loading="lazy" src="https://afar-production.imgix.net/assets/placeholder-image.jpg?lossless=true&amp;auto=compress,format"/></a><a data-gtm-event="article-related-content-module" data-gtm-label="afar" href="/magazine/the-best-independent-bookstores-in-the-united-states"><p class="_1_ZaeXtj-quYjMf326j6fQ">26 Independent Bookstores in the U.S. That We Love</p><p class="_3fN1x6yczF8w06Ji28DAQC"></p><p class="Mw2nv3CiaDiZtjYZfoT0">Books</p></a></div><div class="_20HsJcI5gSjDrdcr6MqId2 _1gZ5uykNxIKtdgx6f9qRf _1ggJ0o9uWv5bOTWfFdkqUH"><a aria-label="13 Movies Set in Paris to Stream Right Now" data-gtm-event="article-related-content-module" data-gtm-label="afar" href="/magazine/movies-about-paris-to-stream-on-netflix-amazon-and-more"><img alt="13 Movies Set in Paris to Stream Right Now" class="rwtN4FvkMLZTY1gX7n3v4 _1MwUyUNFpNtn27W7qYmqk0" data-src="https://afar-production.imgix.net/uploads/content_items/images/RbTh6yRmJ6/original_1c2059469ffff7f3a17bf69beaf59c71.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=top&amp;lossless=true&amp;w=500&amp;h=313" data-srcset="https://afar-production.imgix.net/uploads/content_items/images/RbTh6yRmJ6/original_1c2059469ffff7f3a17bf69beaf59c71.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=top&amp;lossless=true&amp;w=500&amp;h=313&amp;dpr=1 1x,https://afar-production.imgix.net/uploads/content_items/images/RbTh6yRmJ6/original_1c2059469ffff7f3a17bf69beaf59c71.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=top&amp;lossless=true&amp;w=500&amp;h=313&amp;dpr=2 2x,https://afar-production.imgix.net/uploads/content_items/images/RbTh6yRmJ6/original_1c2059469ffff7f3a17bf69beaf59c71.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=top&amp;lossless=true&amp;w=500&amp;h=313&amp;dpr=3 3x" loading="lazy" src="https://afar-production.imgix.net/assets/placeholder-image.jpg?lossless=true&amp;auto=compress,format"/></a><a data-gtm-event="article-related-content-module" data-gtm-label="afar" href="/magazine/movies-about-paris-to-stream-on-netflix-amazon-and-more"><p class="_1_ZaeXtj-quYjMf326j6fQ">13 Movies Set in Paris to Stream Right Now</p><p class="_3fN1x6yczF8w06Ji28DAQC"></p><p class="Mw2nv3CiaDiZtjYZfoT0">Art + Culture</p></a></div><div class="_20HsJcI5gSjDrdcr6MqId2 _1gZ5uykNxIKtdgx6f9qRf _1ggJ0o9uWv5bOTWfFdkqUH"><a aria-label="The Best New Hotels in the World: The Stay List" data-gtm-event="article-related-content-module" data-gtm-label="afar" href="https://www.afar.com/magazine/best-new-hotels"><img alt="The Best New Hotels in the World: The Stay List" class="rwtN4FvkMLZTY1gX7n3v4 _1MwUyUNFpNtn27W7qYmqk0" data-src="https://afar-production.imgix.net/uploads/content_items/images/5QG7mHlVyJ/original_original_KACHI1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=top&amp;lossless=true&amp;w=500&amp;h=313" data-srcset="https://afar-production.imgix.net/uploads/content_items/images/5QG7mHlVyJ/original_original_KACHI1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=top&amp;lossless=true&amp;w=500&amp;h=313&amp;dpr=1 1x,https://afar-production.imgix.net/uploads/content_items/images/5QG7mHlVyJ/original_original_KACHI1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=top&amp;lossless=true&amp;w=500&amp;h=313&amp;dpr=2 2x,https://afar-production.imgix.net/uploads/content_items/images/5QG7mHlVyJ/original_original_KACHI1.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=top&amp;lossless=true&amp;w=500&amp;h=313&amp;dpr=3 3x" loading="lazy" src="https://afar-production.imgix.net/assets/placeholder-image.jpg?lossless=true&amp;auto=compress,format"/></a><a data-gtm-event="article-related-content-module" data-gtm-label="afar" href="https://www.afar.com/magazine/best-new-hotels"><p class="_1_ZaeXtj-quYjMf326j6fQ">The Best New Hotels in the World: The Stay List</p><p class="_3fN1x6yczF8w06Ji28DAQC"></p><p class="Mw2nv3CiaDiZtjYZfoT0"></p></a></div></div></div></div><div class="_1D8IJplksLz6JP4kSPTMY4 _3UsvR5XWVLKCZMVJS5BiWA"><button class="_15VcGn7m1MTuY_EdSlkQjW" type="button"><i class="_1xxwKoVqAaQ7FYmg-3h6Z9 _35bmBoSuCAT15yvvIzfPVV"></i></button><div class="_1idBj71TQVPU78JmUmINCH _3xZf5JXG5Q0sMG7o-bkXQy _3wcIc2Iqzhd3gyDT4nMprE"><span></span></div></div><footer class="_2KRDFnBa-aYol7wyxHPtgF"><div class="_3MCyva0AOS8VF79-N_xhPV"><a class="sTJJ-ZrwICUqbSN7_HVZc" aria-label="AFAR media&#x27;s home page" href="https://www.afar.com"><span class="_3JoBGZnkaYaT1MWbeEf617"></span></a></div><div><a aria-label="Follow us on Facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/AfarMedia" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><i class="_1xxwKoVqAaQ7FYmg-3h6Z9 _2_deLbIhfY1iDKDSDryS8l ISr7lt8794eDFdzeYWpU3 aM4HIu5mC8GbPLZj_u6IF"></i></a><a aria-label="Follow us on Twitter" href="https://www.twitter.com/AFARmedia" re